{"arkId":"cl010113367","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113367","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Cylindre : le Triomphe de David","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cylindre : le Triomphe de David"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1630 - 1667","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 527 - Adolphe Rothschild, Vitrine 6","room":"Salle 527, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1630,"endYear":1667,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Heschler, David","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1611","place":"Memmingen","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1667","place":"Ulm","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q26726773"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"CL 20827","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"chope","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Sans monture ni fond, cylindre destin\u00e9 \u00e0 une chope. La composition se d\u00e9roule d\u0027une mani\u00e8re sym\u00e9trique et lin\u00e9aire autour de la figure du jeune David portant la t\u00eate de Goliath sur la pointe d\u0027un cimeterre. Le vainqueur est suivi d\u0027un cavalier et de quatre soldats \u00e0 pied, tandis que cinq jeunes filles, accompagn\u00e9es d\u0027un enfant et d\u0027un petit chien l\u0027accueillent au son du cornet, du luth et des chants. Sc\u00e8ne inspir\u00e9e du retour de Jepht\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Composition frontale avec deux extremit\u00e9s, sans effort de faire tourner la composition tout autour du cylindre, le groupe des danseuses n